## Learning Center - Documentation and Video Tutorials
As of version 6.1, the Learning Center is available with video tutorials and written documentation. The Learning Center can be opened via the title bar by clicking on the "?" Icon.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

## Video Tutorials
The video instructions are divided into different topics such as *Welcome *or *Learning Basics*. Under *Learning Basics *you will find video instructions for the standard elements, dynamic elements and many other topics that are constantly being updated.

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

## Missing Shortcuts
The following shortcuts are NOT available in the current version:

**Shift + Ctrl + S**

**Save file as**

Alt + Shift + I

Insertion Points

Alt + Shift + U

Updates

Alt + Shift + T

Tools

Alt + Shift + P

Problem Events

Alt + Up

Move up (same level in Outline)

Alt + Down

Move down (same level in Outline)

Ctrl + Shift + Up

Move up as child

Ctrl + Shift + Down

Move down as child

Alt + Shift + Up

Move up as parent

Alt + Shift + Down

Move down as parent

Ctrl + K

Close opened tab

**Shift + Ctrl + S**

**Save file as**

Alt + Ctrl + K

Close all opened tabs

Alt + Shift + D

Data Input

Alt + Shift + O

Output Configuration

## Documentation
The written full documentation can be found in the left area of the Learning Center.

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)

You can read the documentation directly in Business Designer and search for content on the left, or you can open the PDF or HTML documentation in the upper right area.

![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
